238
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:27,960
[SPEAKER_06] A, mislim ba. Moje pitanje, tko je lup?

239
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:30,960
[SPEAKER_03] Mislim da se, da se ovo pitanje.

240
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:38,960
