266
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:10,960
[SPEAKER_03] Hvala.

267
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:11,960
[UNKNOWN] Hvala.

268
00:37:11,960 --> 00:37:21,960
[SPEAKER_01] Se hvala gospođi Velja Gracin, te ofisodice, evo, pisali imate liče.

269
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:23,960
