676
01:22:33,399 --> 01:22:35,399
[SPEAKER_09] Bakirima.

677
01:22:35,399 --> 01:22:36,399
[SPEAKER_09] Bakirima.

678
01:22:36,399 --> 01:22:37,399
[SPEAKER_09] Bakirima.

679
01:22:37,399 --> 01:22:39,399
