684
01:22:55,399 --> 01:22:57,399
[SPEAKER_09] Točno, i to je časno odvijelo.

685
01:22:57,399 --> 01:22:58,399
[SPEAKER_09] To je, da.

686
01:22:58,399 --> 01:22:59,399
[SPEAKER_09] To je, da.

687
01:22:59,399 --> 01:23:01,399
