01:27:01,399 --> 01:27:05,399
[SPEAKER_03] jer to isto imate neka pravila, mi smo to zaista radili.

746
01:27:05,399 --> 01:27:09,399
[SPEAKER_03] I žao nam je bilo i u jednom trenutku da nisu to...

747
01:27:09,399 --> 01:27:12,399
