825
01:30:41,399 --> 01:30:43,399
[SPEAKER_11] I sprpljivati pravi.

826
01:30:43,399 --> 01:30:47,399
[SPEAKER_11] A vi ne služite.

827
01:30:47,399 --> 01:30:49,399
[SPEAKER_11] A vi ne služite.

828
01:30:49,399 --> 01:30:51,399
[SPEAKER_11] U pravosti, vi treba pravni kut

829
01:30:51,399 --> 01:30:53,399
[SPEAKER_11] sebi istrpiti.

830
